A New Organizational Structure


Managing organizations
Visual
James E. Heppelmann Michael E. Porter




Smart, connected products require functions within manufacturing firms to collaborate in new ways. As a result, firms’ structures are rapidly evolving. A new unit focused on data management is starting to appear. Though rare, units focused on ongoing product development and customer success are also starting to be recognized.


